Discover how to get into sport!
Everyone deserves a place in sport, which is why, in partnership with the Australian Sports Commission, Watergardens is giving away a $100 gift card each week to help you get involved—whether as a volunteer, coach, official or participant. Play Area
Sit back and relax, enjoy a lovely break playing in The Marketplace or bask in the sunshine at our brand-new outdoor kids’ playground in Station Street. The kids can make new friends and create their own adventures in our playgrounds, while you can savour a freshly brewed coffee or tea from the sidelines.
